---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy - CodeReserve">
  <section>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> February 2026</p>

    <h2>What We Collect</h2>
    <p>When you use CodeReserve, we collect:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>GitHub account data:</strong> Username, email, avatar URL, and account ID (via GitHub OAuth)</li>
      <li><strong>Repository data:</strong> Repository names and IDs for repos where you install our GitHub App</li>
      <li><strong>Pull request data:</strong> PR numbers, titles, and author information for PRs in protected repos</li>
      <li><strong>Wallet addresses:</strong> If you connect a wallet to make deposits</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use It</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Calculate reputation scores for PR authors</li>
      <li>Process deposits and refunds</li>
      <li>Display your activity in the dashboard</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>What We Don't Do</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>We don't sell your data</li>
      <li>We don't share your data with third parties (except GitHub for OAuth)</li>
      <li>We don't track you across websites</li>
      <li>We don't use cookies for advertising</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Storage</h2>
    <p>Your data is stored securely. Sensitive information like access tokens is encrypted.</p>

    <h2>Data Deletion</h2>
    <p>To delete your data, uninstall the GitHub App from your repositories and email us at dohkku@codereserve.org.</p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>Questions? Email <a href="mailto:dohkku@codereserve.org">dohkku@codereserve.org</a></p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

